lule.hunkar.provincesofcanada

Class Country

  • java.lang.Object
    • lule.hunkar.provincesofcanada.Country

  • public class Country
extends java.lang.Object
    Country class creates specified Country object. It provides method to print to details of the porvinces which a country object holds. Also it provides a method to count the number of provinces, which has a population between specified minimum and maximum values, for a country object. model object.

    Hunkar Lule
